# of copying the same Makefile into separate project directories, include
# it by only copying the template and adjusting the appropriate values.
#
# Original:

# Hey Emacs, this is a -*- makefile -*-
#
# WinAVR makefile written by Eric B. Weddington, Jörg Wunsch, et al.
# Released to the Public Domain
